INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES('379', '1', '2012-09-05 22:37:03', '2012-09-05 22:37:03', '<em>Going beyond protective hearing, even when we have already suffered a hearing loss, we still need to be diligent to protect the hearing that we still have. The longer you go without treatment the more likely serious problems may occur, such as regression. Establish a relationship with hearing provider – get regular check ups and adjustments to get the most out of your ears and your equipment. </em>\r\n\r\nSome signs of a hearing problem:\r\n<div class=\"columns\">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Inability to hear people clearly.</li>\r\n	<li>People seem to mumble and you miss parts of a conversation.</li>\r\n	<li>Frequent requests for repetition or clarification.</li>\r\n	<li>Tendency to need to stare at people when they are talking in order to make it easier to understand what they are saying.</li>\r\n	<li>Fatigue at the end of the day from straining to hear.</li>\r\n	<li>Avoidance of social situations</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Avoidance of noisy environments and excessive background noise.</li>\r\n	<li>Slight ringing in your ears.</li>\r\n	<li>TV goes louder and louder.</li>\r\n	<li>Telephone becomes difficult to talk on.</li>\r\n	<li>Tendency to pretend that you heard someone.</li>\r\n	<li>Fear and embarrassment when asking people to repeat themselves.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"clear: both; margin-top: 20px;\">Denial, or minimizing a hearing loss, frequently occurs. People incorrectly associate it with aging and disability. They simply ask people to talk louder or repeat themselves. Some are apprehensive about the challenge of learning how to use and insert a sophisticated, miniature electronic device. Others may feel shame and embarrassment about wearing a hearing instrument, and will put it off until the distortion has grown so much that they can\'t understand some conversations at all. When hearing impaired individuals accept the advantages of hearing aids, they are amazed at how much they were unknowingly missing in life.</p>', 'Hearing Loss Prevention', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hearing-loss-prevention', '', '', '2012-10-11 17:18:44', '2012-10-11 17:18:44', '', '352', 'http://agdev.ca/crystalhearing/?page_id=379', '0', 'page', '', '0');
