lad too! I could go on but I think you get the message that I am very grateful, not just for the hearing aids, but for the kind and willing way you help me with whatever problem I may be having and for your promise of ongoing help whenever I need it. So thank you very much for making this experience a pleasant one. I hope you will be able to help a lot of people who have hearing loss and need someone to guide them through the process of hearing aids.\r\n\r\n<strong>- Bee Pepper</strong>', 'Testimonials', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '884-revision-12', '', '', '2012-10-30 20:33:26', '2012-10-30 20:33:26', '', '884', 'http://agdev.ca/crystalhearing/884-revision-12/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
